Toyota to Create More Safety Oversight Positions After Recalls

-- B y   M a k i k o   K i t a m u r a   a n d   M a s a t s u g u   H o r i e
-- 
2011-02-24T03:09:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/toyota-to-create-more-safety-oversight-positions-after-recalls.html
  Toyota Motor Corp . may add more
management positions overseeing safety after the world’s largest
automaker made record recalls.  The new positions may report to one or more Toyota
operating officers who would work alongside the company’s chief
quality officers in each major region, spokeswoman  Shiori Hashimoto  said by phone today.  The news was reported earlier today by the Wall Street
Journal.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Makiko Kitamura in Tokyo at 
 mkitamura1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kae Inoue at 
 kinoue@bloomberg.net  